<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 21 May 2026 06:46:17 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a0eaa347450a</link><description>&lt;p&gt;⛩️🦊 京都 - 伏见稻荷大社。（Inariyamakan-yuchi）&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="At a Japanese shrine looking down a stone path passing through hundreds of red wooden arches evenly spaced only a few inches apart. Each arch is inscribed with black text." height="4160" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/nfd/6a0eaa347450a.jpg" width="6240"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://nfd.some.pics"&gt;@nfd&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2026 06:46:17 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a0ea2493aae8</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一株可爱的布列氏石莲花正在开花（在加州克莱蒙特的加州植物园）。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="An outdoor, eye-level shot captures a blooming succulent with a dense, pale green rosette at its base, growing out of wood chip mulch. Multiple tall, curving flower stalks erupt upwards and outwards in a fan shape, displaying a gradient of colors from peach and pink to bright reddish-pink stems topped with clusters of small, yellowish-green buds. In the background, a large grey boulder sits on the upper left, surrounded by dry soil and sparse, low-growing green and silvery-green wild shrubs under bright, direct sunlight.
" height="1505" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/sjwallin/6a0ea2493aae8.jpg" width="1128"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://sjwallin.some.pics"&gt;@sjwallin&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2026 06:12:28 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a0e3564a6310</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一只看起来受惊的玳瑁加白猫躺在木地板上，表情略显烦躁。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Startled-looking tortico cat laying on a wood floor looking slightly annoyed." height="1332" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/hp/6a0e3564a6310.jpg" width="2000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://hp.some.pics"&gt;@hp&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 22:27:55 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a0e35462b15b</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一只玳瑁猫在紫色床上打盹。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Tortico cat snoozing in a purple bed." height="1332" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/hp/6a0e35462b15b.jpg" width="2000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://hp.some.pics"&gt;@hp&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 22:27:23 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>马戏团进城</title><link>https://some.pics/6a0e114317302</link><description>&lt;p&gt;马戏团到镇上来了 🎪&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Red and white circus tents with cloudy sky in background " height="7674" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/purplelime/6a0e114317302.jpg" width="5354"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://purplelime.some.pics"&gt;@purplelime&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 19:53:42 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>